    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if it's not just in my head? what if the most loving thing i could actually do is just... stop being the problem? like, if i wasn't there, they wouldn't have to deal with my failures anymore. wouldn't that be a kind of peace for them? to just not have me holding them back?",
