      "content": "Please know that abandoning your children, even in the heat of depression, is illegal and guarantees they a life filled with trauma rather than the peace you fear to give them. The most profound way to remove your \"shadow\" isn't by leaving them to suffer, but by seeking professional help to heal the struggles that drive these thoughts. True freedom for your family comes from facing these feelings together with a therapist or support group, ensuring they grow up with a parent who might struggle but is there for them.",
